<p>That&#x27;s because the % operator in java isn&#x27;t an arithmetic modulo as it would seem to be.  <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modular_arithmetic#Remainders" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modular_arithmetic#Remainders</a> (3rd paragraph). </p><p>It&#x27;s Java that is actually wrong in this instance :) </p>
